But, they are being kept secret from the world.  Word is starting to filter out, a leak here a leak there, just rumors, no knows what to believe.  Still, a consensus is starting to form around a single idea, and you are grateful you didn't get the drug.  The truth seems to be that  sixty years after they took the drug they start to lose their minds, and end up in a vegetative state.  It's like Alzheimer's overnight.  The people that took the trial drug, before FDA approval all seem to be exhibiting this zombie like state. Still, a consensus is starting to form around a single idea, and you are grateful you didn't get the drug. The people that took the trial drug, before FDA approval all seem to be exhibiting this zombie like state.  And now this is the destiny for everyone that was given it before their twenty-eighth birthday.  We, the "Lost Generation", have age, but we don't have this doom hanging over us. But, they are being kept secret from the world.  Word is starting to filter out, a leak here a leak there, just rumors, no knows what to believe.  Still, a consensus is starting to form around a single idea, and you are grateful you didn't get the drug.  The truth seems to be that  sixty years after they took the drug they start to lose their minds, and end up in a vegetative state.  It's like Alzheimer's overnight.  The people that took the trial drug, before FDA approval all seem to be exhibiting this zombie like state.  And now this is the destiny for everyone that was given it before their twenty-eighth birthday.  We, the "Lost Generation", have age, but we don't have this doom hanging over us.  In fact because of our status we have been cared for by those that did get the drug, we get the best health care, the best medicines, the best treatments, since those others feel a guilt towards us.  So, it's not so bad being a Lost Generation, most of us feel as if we are still in our forties.  But, the world is doomed, those that care for us will soon be unable to take care of themselves, and we are in no position to repopulate the world.  This is truly the end of man kind, and we brought it
